subject: United States Open (Golf)
Golf
lead_paragraph: By the end of the third round, Tiger Woods was tied for 14th, five strokes behind Jim Furyk and Graeme McDowell, the 2010 champion, who posted a two-under 68 for a 54-hole total of one under.
